 2023-05812023-06-16GAC
ActUnited Nations Act
SubjectRegulations Amending Certain Regulations Made Under the United Nations Act
PrecisRegulations Amending CERTAIN REGULATIONS MADE UNDER THE UNITED NATIONS ACT in order to permit the provision, processing or payment of funds, other financial assets or economic resources, or the provision of goods and services that are necessary to ensure the timely delivery of urgently needed humanitarian assistance or to support other activities related to basic human needs, if provided by certain humanitarian organizations, for 14 countries (Central African Republic, Democratic People's Republic of Korea, Congo, Haiti, Iran, Iraq, Lebanon, Libya, Mali, Somalia, South Sudan, Sudan, Yemen, and ISIL (Da'esh) and Al-Qaida).
RegistrationRegistration: SOR/ 2023-0134 Publication Date: 2023-07-05
